summary: Hopefully you all enjoy this game save as much as I did.
descriptionHtml: This is a game save from a character I have in skyrim, it is a female imperial equipped with full nightingale armour and mehrune's razor, the main questline is completed but there are still loads of side quests to do if you want to, she is level 12, so is a great character if you want to be a sneaky thief or assassin. Also if you would like to request a new game save I would be happy to create one, just say the race, class, level e.g
author: Jman11299
